{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Second, we were 1,800 people on that boat, which, you know, consisted of the transport from the and the transport from the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I think that's All.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know there were 1,800 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the ship probably had place maybe for 200 or 300.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were very few cabins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the cabins were usually occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were a few older people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, the Czech transport had no-- no old people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were all young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were a couple of maybe middle-aged couples, but that was all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Most of the people were in their either teens or 20s or maybe early 30s.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the people from-- from Danzig, they had quite a few old people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also the people from the which-- who were Viennese had quite a few old people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So some of the cabins were assigned to the older people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we just-- I remember I-- I don't think I had a sleeping place for probably four days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were just, you know, running around and-- and bumping into people, shoving and pushing, and just lay down somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Only after several days we found-- I found a place with a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were some bunkers and some planks down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was-- we called it the catacombs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there we-- we finally could put our luggage down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had a rucksack and a little small suitcase.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And sort of-- I-- I think we had-- we had a blanket and there was some straw on-- on those planks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were I don't know how many people in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And you could hear everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
